<Challenge Title="Rectangle and Circle Analyzer">
    <Text>
        In this challenge, you will create a single program that combines the
        functionality of the <b>Rectangle</b> and <b>Circle</b> analyzers.
    </Text>
    <TaskItem Name="Complete Shape Analyzer Guantlet">If you have not done so, complete the <MudButton Variant="Variant.Filled" Color="Color.Primary" Href="@ShapeAnalyzer.PageRef.Href">Guantlet: @ShapeAnalyzer.PageRef.Name</MudButton></TaskItem>
    <ConsoleProjectTask Name="Create Project">Create a new project called "Shape Analyzer"</ConsoleProjectTask>
    <TaskItem Name="Display Welcome">At the start of your program, display a welcome message.</TaskItem>
    <TaskItem Name="Display a Menu">Display a menu with 3 options: Analyze Rectangle, Analyze Circle, Exit</TaskItem>
    <TaskItem Name="Prompt User">Prompt the user to select an option.</TaskItem>
    <TaskItem Name="First Choice">If the user selected "Analyze Rectangle" the <b>Rectangle Analyzer</b> challenge should be exectued.</TaskItem>
    <TaskItem Name="Second Choice">If the user selected "Analyze Circle" the <b>Circle Analyzer</b> challenge should be exectued.</TaskItem>
    <TaskItem Name="Exit Choice">If the user selected "Exit" your program should display a nice "Goodbye message"</TaskItem>
    <TaskItem Name="Invalid Choice">If the user made an invalid choice, the program should display "Invalid option. Goodbye!"</TaskItem>
</Challenge>